  "description": "Makes ingots more trapezoid",
  "body": "<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pgyqtQ5.png\" alt=\"Trapezoid Ingots\" width=\"544\" height=\"168\" /></h1>\n<h3>Small texture pack by yo314159at that makes ingots more trapezoid</h3>\n<br />\n<p><a href=\"./trapezoid-ingots/version/1.21.x-vanilla\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nXSsrkD.png\" alt=\"Vanilla\" width=\"197\" height=\"48\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>(Iron Ingot, Gold Ingot, Copper Ingot, Netherite Ingot)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8c4oNeN.png\" width=\"667\" height=\"381\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"./trapezoid-ingots/version/1.18.x-mods\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UVfjHJ2.png\" alt=\"Mod Support\" width=\"292\" height=\"48\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>All vanilla ingots</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/botania\">Botania</a> (Manasteel Ingot, Elementium Ingot, Terrasteel Ingot, Gaia Spirit Ingot)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/create\">Create</a> (Brass Ingot, Copper Ingot, Zinc Ingot)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/aquaculture\">Aquaculture 2</a> (Neptunium Ingot)<br /></li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p>Might add support for more mods, depending on demand.</p>\n<p>Feel free to request a version port <a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/yo314159at.bsky.social\">@yo314159at</a> if I haven't made it already.</p>",
